               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Ḥāshīyah-'i Kashf al-maḥjūb by ʻAbd al-Ghafūr Lārī, -1506</summary>
                  <msItem class="https://lccn.loc.gov/sh85129649" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_988-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Notes on selected passages of the 
                <title key="work_21821">Kashf al-maḥjūb</title>(کشف المحجوب) by 
                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_166217879" role="aut">ʻAlī ibn ʻUsmān Hujvīrī</persName>. The author, ʻAbd al-Ghafūr, is presumably to be identified with the well-known Naqshbandi author ʻAbd al-Ghafūr Raz̤ī al-Dīn Lārī (d. 956/1506-7).
                        </p>
                        <p>15 lines per page; nastaʻliq; copyist, 
                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f8012" role="scr">Muḥibb ʻAlī ibn Z̤iyāʼ al-Dīn</persName>; rubrications; many marginal notes; worm-eaten and water-stained.
                        </p>
                        <p>Dated 15 Jumādá II 1088 (15 Aug 1677).</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658778.0x000001 viaf_78148995935359751416" type="standard">ʻAbd al-Ghafūr Lārī, -1506</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658778.0x000001 viaf_78148995935359751416">لارى، عبد الغفور</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_21821">Hāshiyah-'i Kashf al-maḥjūb</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_21821">حاشیهٔ کشف المحجوب</title>
                  </msItem>
